data.description: If you are looking for wide open spaces, you have finally found it!  The seller is offering a $3000 concession for flooring replacement and an additional $5000 towards rate buydown or closing costs!!!  This home is a 3 bedroom/2bathroom, 1809 square foot home that offers multiple living spaces. The den is huge and features all new vinyl flooring throughout. The primary bedroom is spacious with a big walk-in closet and a 5-piece primary bathroom. There are two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom. Enjoy winter weather in your den that has an electric fireplace to keep you warm and is open to the updated kitchen. There are tons of storage as well as a huge pantry. The laundry room is conveniently located here as well. There is a large, enclosed patio that would be perfect for a game room or workout room. There is a large chicken, coop, an oversized 2 car garage plus, an enclosed storage shed that was used for a tack room and an animal lean-to. Did I also mention that this home is located on 2.45 acres! It is completely fenced with multiple paddocks for your animals. There are many fruit trees on the property as well. The roof was replaced 5 years ago, and the HVAC system was replaced in March 2023. The home is on Morgan County Quality water and the monthly bills are low.  This home has a lot to offer for the price plus NO HOA!
